FORECAST DATA
-------------

NOAA Global Forecast System (GFS) Wave model data
  Source: U.S. National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration (NOAA)
          National Centers for Environmental Prediction (NCEP)
  Access:  https://nomads.ncep.noaa.gov/
  Notes:   U.S. Government work. This project downloads GRIB2 files via HTTPS.
           Users of derived forecast maps should not treat them as official
           NOAA/NWS products. See NOAA and NWS terms of use for data policies.


